data.description: This beautiful almost 2700 Sqft home is located in the El Dorado Country View Estates neighborhood just above Mission lakes. The Bella model floor plan is a spacious and open layout including 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and optional 4th bedroom/office in the main home and a separate, attached, casita with its own entrance and bedroom and bath. Large private master suite features a soaking tub and separate shower, double vanity and a large walk-in closet and sliding doors out to the backyard. Second bedroom is also considered a master with walk-in closet and shared bathroom. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining with lots of cabinet space, granite countertops, room for a dining table and a huge island that opens up to the living room area. This living area has a beautiful fireplace to enjoy during the cooler nights and is light and bright with lots of windows and a sliding door to the private yard and mountain views. Relax outside and enjoy mountain views with no rear neighbors in this quiet and peaceful setting. Bring your boats and RV’s to park behind the big double metal gated side yard with RV hookups. There are NO HOMEOWNER DUES in this neighborhood but you are located close to the Mission lakes country club 18-hole golf course, and a short drive to local shops and Palm Springs while up the hill is nearby Joshua Tree. This home has lots to offer so check it out.
